\newlabel{tab:patent-diagnosis-compact}{{3}{12}{Compact \AUPRC {} summary behind the patent diagnosis for the five-model comparison panel. Values are mean $\pm $ seed std over the matched 3-seed runs. The tiny 2021 slice is pooled into the \texttt {2020--2021} stratum to avoid over-interpreting a 72-example cell}{table.3}{}}
\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {2}{\ignorespaces Patent temporal/provenance diagnosis in terms of mean AUPRC{} for the five-model comparison panel. Left: pooled year-band slices, with 2021 merged into the recent stratum. Right: test-set overlap buckets computed from the saved overlap score. Error bars denote seed std over the matched 3-seed runs. \texttt  {RF} dominates the aggregate temporal benchmark, while \texttt  {DTI-LM} remains strongest only in the lowest-overlap bucket}}{12}{figure.2}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:patent-diagnosis}{{2}{12}{Patent temporal/provenance diagnosis in terms of mean \AUPRC {} for the five-model comparison panel. Left: pooled year-band slices, with 2021 merged into the recent stratum. Right: test-set overlap buckets computed from the saved overlap score. Error bars denote seed std over the matched 3-seed runs. \texttt {RF} dominates the aggregate temporal benchmark, while \texttt {DTI-LM} remains strongest only in the lowest-overlap bucket}{figure.2}{}}
